{"tid":1444531,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係所有合作運動都係值得搞","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:33.000Z","uid":197980,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec119be3e2e163b9bfb01801d9e5df4a65954753","tid":1444531,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"例如塞鐵，佔紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話要個運動成功就一定要有犧牲，班淺黃至深藍嘅人唔會諗咁多，唔會諗背後動機，佢哋有人係好蠢，好自私，淨係會諗住自己個飯碗。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋反送中係因為條條例會令外資會撤，經濟會崩潰，搞到佢個飯碗先出嚟。當有人搞不合作， 又搞到佢個飯碗，佢哋又會轉風向。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭見你塞鐵其實係樂見其成，唔洗做嘢就分化到我哋，因為一定有受影響嘅人對不滿做法，打手都唔洗請，示威者自燃。又有淺黃變中立。<br />\n<br />\n發起不合作之前請諗下成效同代價，而目標係政府，癱瘓政府部門又或者有人提出其他方法都可以拎嚟討論研究下。<br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係睇連登就覺得自己一直佔民意上風，抗爭嘅人唔只係得連登仔。"},{"pid":"b2bc21b061ba352f1a60e7ae39df656db513118d","tid":1444531,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833b53e261103e53a3aed3445885b903f717147d","tid":1444531,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2de86cfcb975ad09e61d3db386122001c88139","tid":1444531,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3d344f7d9785454e44aa0d9414aff78c20036b","tid":1444531,"uid":302028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6498a97bddc0193e623b2038765a25de9cd1c1be","tid":1444531,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />